Goodmorning #Pakistan and #JummahMubarak 😊

Yesterday your #PMImranKhan took  his #Covid19 #Vaccine and I think he is sending two important messages:

1. He leads with example. He got the shot when others in his age group did.

2. He shows you what to do: #GetVaccinated! https://t.co/QSMrQXaxkh
